Game Control System

Hierarchy:
    -Digilab:       Emergency use, ignores rules and permissions and exectues command

    -Discord:       Admin, is allowed to exectues commands and confirms requests from       
                    Minecraft
    
    -Minecraft:     User, can send command requests to the discord bot, which have to be 
                    allowed by a user on discord

Example:            When a Player types a command, for example: request is sent to          
                    discord-bot and needs to be allowed or declined with a command on discord, for example: !confirm or !deny   

Raspberry Pi:       -upon a request being sent, the display lists the command that is 
                    requested 